---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import CTAButton from '../../../components/CTAButton.astro';
import { COMPANY_INFO } from '../../../utils/constants';

const lang = 'en';
const post = {
  title: 'Prime Mover Bad Credit 2026: Financing Available Despite Poor Credit Score',
  slug: 'prime-mover-bad-credit-2026',
  excerpt: 'Get prime mover financing even with bad credit. We look at business viability, not just credit score. 0% down payment available for transport operators.',
  date: '2026-01-08',
  author: 'Ing Heng Credit Team',
  readTime: 6,
  category: 'Transport Vehicles',
  image: '/images/blog/prime-mover-financing.jpg'
};

const keywords = ['bad credit truck financing', 'prime mover poor credit', 'CTOS rejection', '0% down payment', 'transport business loan'],
  breadcrumbItems = [
  { label: 'Home', href: '/en' },
  { label: 'Blog', href: '/en/blog' },
  { label: post.title, href: `/en/blog/${post.slug}` }
];
---

<BaseLayout title={post.title} description={post.excerpt} lang={lang} keywords={keywords}>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "BlogPosting",
      "headline": post.title,
      "description": post.excerpt,
      "datePublished": post.date,
      "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": post.author },
      "publisher": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "Ing Heng Credit & Leasing Sdn Bhd",
        "logo": {
          "@type": "ImageObject",
          "url": "https://inghengcredit.com/logo.png"
        }
      }
    }
  </script>

  <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbItems} />

  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <header class="mb-8">
      <span class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #D4A574;">Transport Vehicles</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2" style="color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase;">{post.title}</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">{post.excerpt}</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">
        <span>{post.author}</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <time>{new Date(post.date).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</time>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>{post.readTime} min read</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h2>Bad Credit? You Can Still Get Prime Mover Financing</h2>

      <p>Banks reject prime mover financing if CTOS score below 650. Past bankruptcy, late payments, or defaults mean automatic rejection. But your transport business needs trucks to operate. Ing Heng Credit looks at business viability, not just credit score.</p>

      <h2>Why Banks Reject Bad Credit</h2>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>CTOS Score Below 650:</strong> Automatic rejection</li>
        <li><strong>Past Bankruptcy:</strong> 7-year black mark</li>
        <li><strong>Late Payment History:</strong> Shows risk</li>
        <li><strong>Existing Defaults:</strong> High debt ratio</li>
        <li><strong>New Business:</strong> No track record</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Our Approach: Business Viability First</h2>

      <p>We evaluate based on business health, not just credit score:</p>

      <h3>What We Consider</h3>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Current Revenue:</strong> Business generating money now?</li>
        <li><strong>Contracts:</strong> Signed agreements with clients?</li>
        <li><strong>Route Profitability:</strong> Are operations profitable?</li>
        <li><strong>Experience:</strong> How long in transport industry?</li>
        <li><strong>Asset Value:</strong> Trucks have resale value?</li>
        <li><strong>Character:</strong> References, business reputation</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Financing Options for Bad Credit</h2>

      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Situation</th>
            <th>Bank</th>
            <th>Ing Heng</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>CTOS below 650</td>
            <td>Rejected</td>
            <td>Considered</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Past bankruptcy</td>
            <td>Rejected</td>
            <td>Case-by-case</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Late payments</td>
            <td>Rejected</td>
            <td>Acceptable with reason</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>New business</td>
            <td>Rejected</td>
            <td>Evaluated on contracts</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h2>Higher Down Payment Not Required</h2>

      <p>Some lenders charge higher down payment for bad credit:
  <br>• 20-30% down payment
  <br>• Higher interest rates
  <br>• Shorter terms</p>

      <p><strong>Ing Heng Credit:</strong>
  <br>• 0% down payment regardless of credit
  <br>• Competitive interest rates
  <br>• Standard 3-7 year terms</p>

      <h2>Real Approval Stories</h2>

      <h3>Bankruptcy Discharged - Approved</h3>

      <p>"Bankruptcy discharged 2022. Banks rejected all financing. Needed 2 prime movers to restart transport business. Ing Heng looked at business plan, 3 signed contracts from former clients. Approved both trucks with 0% down. Running 2 years now, never missed payment. Business rebuilt, credit score recovering. Ing Heng gave second chance when banks said no."</p>
      <p><em>— Kumar Raj, Transport Operator</em></p>

      <h3>CTOS 580 - Approved</h3>

      <p>"CTOS score 580 due to credit card defaults during COVID. Business operating 3 years, profitable. Bank rejected prime mover financing due to low score. Ing Heng evaluated business: RM150,000 monthly revenue, growing client base, experienced operator. Approved 1 truck, 0% down. After 6 months of on-time payments, approved second truck. CTOS score now 620 and rising. Business viable, credit score irrelevant."</p>
      <p><em>— Hassan Ali, Owner</em></p>

      <h3>No Credit History - Approved</h3>

      <p>"Started transport business 2023. No CTOS history (new to credit). Banks required 2 years trading record plus guarantor. Ing Heng evaluated business: 5 signed contracts with logistics companies, experienced drivers, proven routes. Approved 3 prime movers, 0% down. 18 months later, running 5 trucks, excellent payment history. Built business and credit simultaneously."</p>
      <p><em>— David Tan, Entrepreneur</em></p>

      <h2>Requirements: Bad Credit Financing</h2>

      <h3>What We Need</h3>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Business Registration:</strong> Valid SSM</li>
        <li><strong>Bank Statements:</strong> 6-12 months showing revenue</li>
        <li><strong>Contracts:</strong> Signed agreements with clients</li>
        <li><strong>Business Plan:</strong> How trucks will generate income</li>
        <li><strong>References:</strong> Client or supplier references</li>
        <li><strong>Driver Info:</strong> Valid licenses</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>What Helps Approval</h3>

      <ul>
        <li>Consistent monthly revenue</li>
        <td>Long-term client contracts</td>
        <li>Industry experience</li>
        <li>Profitable operations</li>
        <li>Professional references</li>
        <li>Collateral (other assets)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Interest Rates</h2>

      <p>Our rates remain competitive even with bad credit:
  <br>• Same rates as standard financing
  <br>• No penalty for credit score
  <br>• Focus on repayment ability, not past history</p>

      <h2>Rebuild Credit While Operating</h2>

      <p>On-time payments to Ing Heng Credit:
  <br>• Reported to CTOS monthly
  <br>• Improves credit score over time
  <br>• Refinance to better rates later
  <br>• Access bank financing in future</p>

      <h2>Step-by-Step Application</h2>

      <p><strong>Day 1:</strong> Submit application with bad credit explanation
  <br><strong>Day 2:</strong> We review business viability
  <br><strong>Day 3:</strong> Approval (subject to business health)
  <br><strong>Day 4-7:</strong> Documentation
  <br><strong>Day 8-14:</strong> Truck acquisition</p>

      <h2>Ing Heng Credit: Bad Credit Specialist</h2>

      <ul>
        <li>Look at business, not just score</li>
        <li>0% down payment for all credit levels</li>
        <li>Fast 24-48 hour approval</li>
        <li>Help rebuild credit through payments</li>
        <li>Second chance financing available</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>The Bottom Line</h2>

      <p>Bad credit doesn't mean your transport business can't grow. If business is viable, generating revenue, with growth potential, we finance prime movers. 0% down payment preserves cash. Fast approval gets trucks on road.</p>

      <div style="background: #F5F0E8; border-left: 4px solid #D4A574; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <h3 style="color: #2D1810; margin-top: 0;">Bad Credit? We Can Help</h3>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">0% down prime mover financing. Approved based on business viability.</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0;"><strong>Contact:</strong> +60175700889 (WhatsApp) | 03-3324 8899 (Phone)</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t">
      <CTAButton text="Get Bad Credit Financing" link={COMPANY_INFO.whatsapp.link} variant="accent" size="large" />
    </footer>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h2 { color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 2rem; margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 3px solid #D4A574; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  h3 { color: #8B6F47; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  p { line-height: 1.8; color: #374151; }
  strong { color: #2D1810; font-weight: 700; }
  ul { list-style: none; padding-left: 0; }
  li { padding-left: 1.5rem; position: relative; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #374151; }
  li::before { content: '✓'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #D4A574; font-weight: bold; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1.5rem 0; }
  th { background: #2D1810; color: #F5F0E8; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left; }
  td { border: 1px solid #E5E7EB; padding: 0.75rem; }
  em { display: block; margin-top: 0.5rem; color: #6B7280; font-style: normal; }
  br { display: none; }
</style>
